_sText: WELCOME ABOARD :) A nice aim map hi made with help from the map de_port by Valve. It can also be played with GunGame Style Both teams spawn at the ship, if you go on the water you will instantly die. Terrors can go on the top, by goin on the side passage right at the side of their spawn. The rest you can see it for your selves. You may have to type this command in console "r_3dsky 1" So you can see the sea. (I made it skybox cuz of the lagg) This map tooked 5 Hours. I hope you Play it & Have Fun.
